---
import { siteData } from '../data/site.ts';
---

<section id="produtos" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-neutral-light">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-accent-amber/10 text-accent-amber font-semibold rounded-full text-sm mb-4">
        Como Funciona
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-6 leading-tight">
        Coloque o visitante na rota certa
        <span class="text-primary-blue">
          em 3 passos
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Um processo simples, com começo, meio e fim, para aumentar aproveitamento do destino e receita por visita.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      {siteData.products.map((product, index) => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-blue text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl shadow-lg mb-6">
            {index + 1}
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-3">{product.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            {product.description}
          </p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-blue/10 text-primary-blue font-semibold rounded-full text-sm mb-4">
          Diferencial Estratégico
        </span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-4">
          Muito além de um simples <span class="text-primary-blue">cadastro de locais</span>.
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Nossa solução é focada em ampliar a inteligência geográfica do seu empreendimento, utilizando o algoritmo do Google Maps a seu favor.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 bg-primary-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Aumentar visibilidade orgânica em buscas locais</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 bg-primary-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Ampliar o alcance de buscas relacionadas ao seu setor</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 bg-primary-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Gerar tráfego qualificado de visitantes com intenção real</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 bg-primary-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span>Fortalecer a autoridade digital do seu empreendimento</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a
            href="#contato"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-primary-blue hover:bg-primary-darkblue text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition-all duration-200 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-center w-full sm:w-auto"
          >
            Solicitar análise gratuita
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-accent-amber/10 text-accent-amber font-semibold rounded-full text-sm mb-4">
          O que você recebe
        </span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-4">
          Uma infraestrutura de descoberta <span class="text-primary-blue">completa e otimizada</span>.
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-5">
          {siteData.products.map((product) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-blue/10 text-primary-blue rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-xl">
                {product.icon}
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-neutral-dark">{product.title}</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">{product.description}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
